  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to H.A.S 2207, <strong>Overseer</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESIGN YOUR OWN ROCKETS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f2c3a924f892c49527d040201603397.poster.avif?t=1757039957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f2c3a924f892c49527d040201603397.webm?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f2c3a924f892c49527d040201603397.mp4?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In HAS Galactics, you will be able to design your own rockets. Chose from a wide variety of parts that will unlock as you progress. The more advanced your rocket is, the more daring mission you will be able to accomplish, but it also brings risks. Make sure to plan your launch to maximise your chance of success!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag and drop parts, make sure to have enough fuel tanks and enough power to reach outer space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AUTOMATE PRODUCTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/9814c090078ead37fb566bf437ca713a.poster.avif?t=1757039957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/9814c090078ead37fb566bf437ca713a.webm?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/9814c090078ead37fb566bf437ca713a.mp4?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To build the rockets you designed, you will have to automate their production. Start small, from basic ores, and progress to assembling advanced rocket fuel and supercomputers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place belts, split and merge to have the most efficient design, add more miners to produce more and smelters to build faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FULFILL CONTRACTS FROM THE FACTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/02a0a89ab87e42023e0a7bcfd019fd09.poster.avif?t=1757039957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/02a0a89ab87e42023e0a7bcfd019fd09.webm?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/02a0a89ab87e42023e0a7bcfd019fd09.mp4?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In HAS Galactics, factions are your source of income and technology progress, through contracts. Each contract will have an impact on your reputation with each.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Careful plan your contracts and unlock advanced technologies and upgrade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>So... Are you ready, Overseer?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f22af6b9f4aec328a62836fdde86441.poster.avif?t=1757039957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f22af6b9f4aec328a62836fdde86441.webm?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f22af6b9f4aec328a62836fdde86441.mp4?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features <br>✅ Design, assemble and launch rockets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Build production lines and manage your resources</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Research new technologies and improve efficiency</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Accept missions from powerful intergalactic corporations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Explore what this world has to offer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to H.A.S 2207, <strong>Overseer</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESIGN YOUR OWN ROCKETS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f2c3a924f892c49527d040201603397.poster.avif?t=1757039957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f2c3a924f892c49527d040201603397.webm?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f2c3a924f892c49527d040201603397.mp4?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In HAS Galactics, you will be able to design your own rockets. Chose from a wide variety of parts that will unlock as you progress. The more advanced your rocket is, the more daring mission you will be able to accomplish, but it also brings risks. Make sure to plan your launch to maximise your chance of success!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag and drop parts, make sure to have enough fuel tanks and enough power to reach outer space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AUTOMATE PRODUCTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/9814c090078ead37fb566bf437ca713a.poster.avif?t=1757039957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/9814c090078ead37fb566bf437ca713a.webm?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/9814c090078ead37fb566bf437ca713a.mp4?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To build the rockets you designed, you will have to automate their production. Start small, from basic ores, and progress to assembling advanced rocket fuel and supercomputers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place belts, split and merge to have the most efficient design, add more miners to produce more and smelters to build faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FULFILL CONTRACTS FROM THE FACTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/02a0a89ab87e42023e0a7bcfd019fd09.poster.avif?t=1757039957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/02a0a89ab87e42023e0a7bcfd019fd09.webm?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/02a0a89ab87e42023e0a7bcfd019fd09.mp4?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In HAS Galactics, factions are your source of income and technology progress, through contracts. Each contract will have an impact on your reputation with each.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Careful plan your contracts and unlock advanced technologies and upgrade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>So... Are you ready, Overseer?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f22af6b9f4aec328a62836fdde86441.poster.avif?t=1757039957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f22af6b9f4aec328a62836fdde86441.webm?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732050/extras/1f22af6b9f4aec328a62836fdde86441.mp4?t=1757039957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features <br>✅ Design, assemble and launch rockets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Build production lines and manage your resources</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Research new technologies and improve efficiency</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Accept missions from powerful intergalactic corporations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Explore what this world has to offer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
